title: O'Neill Girls Freeride Coachings presented by K2 & Blue Tomato - Diedamskopf -
description: Our hike & ride coaching at the beautiful Diedamskopf was definitely the most stunning camp we hosted this winter. The girls hiked all day and have been rewarded with empty mountains and fresh powder. It was an epic season and we can't wait to start all over again next winter.
